## VS Code (only track User settings)
dotfiles/.config/Code/*
!dotfiles/.config/Code/User/
dotfiles/.config/Code/User/*
!dotfiles/.config/Code/User/settings.json
!dotfiles/.config/Code/User/keybindings.json

## Sublime Text (only track Preferences)
dotfiles/.config/sublime-text/*
!dotfiles/.config/sublime-text/Packages/
dotfiles/.config/sublime-text/Packages/*
!dotfiles/.config/sublime-text/Packages/User/
dotfiles/.config/sublime-text/Packages/User/*
!dotfiles/.config/sublime-text/Packages/User/Preferences.sublime-settings

